  <summary>2/3/1988--Introduced.
Fixes valuation standards for purposes of mortgage revenue bond purchase price requirements in connection with any ground lease having a remaining term of at least 35 years and a specified ground rent for at least the initial ten years of the term. Requires that pertinent Federal regulations be amended to reflect these standards.</summary>
